Class AdminHomeController

java.lang.Object
view.AdminHomeController
public class AdminHomeController extends Object
Controller class for the Admin Home view. This class handles user management functionalities such as creating, deleting users, and logging out from the admin interface.
Author:
Reuben Thomas, Ryan Zaken
